{"word":"λυσσώδης","slug":"λυσσώδης","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>λυσσώδης</b></el> <el>(λυσς-ώδης, ες) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:εἶδος'><el>εἶδος</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>like one raging, frantic</i>, of martial rage, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>of madness</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}